Eisiligieki Abraham enkayioni


1  Neipang'aki Olaitoriani ninye te mbata oo lkeek oo nyaanyukie lng'abolo te Mamre, etonita te kutukaji olng'obor lenye eirowua enkolong. 
2   Neraposhu inkonyek enyena neing'orisho, naa ng'ura, eitashe iltung'ana okuni te dukuya ninye. Ore pee edol ninche, nepuku akuetu tiatua olng'obor anang'are ninche, neirrugo ninye abaiki enkop ejo: 
3  “Olaitoriani lai, tenanoto omom too nkonyek inono, migiroo ake osinka lino. 
4  Inchoo eyauni enkiti are peyie intukuyieyie inkejek inyi, niyeng'iyeng'ang'a te ntonata olchani. 
5  Naa kayau enkiti daa peyie intokiki aagolu nindimidimi aashom itagolo amu iimutua enetii osinka linyi.” Nejo ninche, “Taasa anaa enitejo.” 
6  Neisarrisar Abraham alo atua olng'obor enetii Sara, nejoki ninye, “Isiosionie imboreitin uni e ntapa napuyiapuy nimpurj aitobir imukateni.” 
7  Neipirri Abraham alo enetii inkishu enyena, nereu olashe onana sidai, neisho olaisiaayiani lenye, meisiosiono aitobir. 
8  Neyau eng'orno, o kule, o ilo ashe onana oitobira airragie te dukuya ninche. Neitashe te mbata ninche te ntonata olchani einosita endaa.


9  Nejoki ninche ninye, “Koree doi Sara enkitok ino?” Neng'amaaa ajoki, 
10   “Etii atua olng'obor.” Nejoki Olaitoriani, “Meeta duoo inchere peyie maarrinyokino iyie te nkata olorujuruj, ore Sara enkitok ino, keaku anaata enkayioni ina kata.” Ore eiro einining'isho ake Sara te nkutuk olng'obor ti oriong e Abraham. 
11  Etaa apa moruak oleng ina kata Abraham o Sara, etaa kituaak oleng, metaa meekure duoo ninye eidim Sara atoiu enkerai. 
12   Nekweni Sara makewan ejo: “Aidipa ataa moruo, netamorua sii ninye olpayian lai, katum nanu murruna?” 
13  Nejoki Olaitoriani Abraham, “Ainyoo doi peyie etakuenia Sara nejo, ‘Kesipa hoo doi ajo kaiu enkerai, nataa taata moruo?’ 
14   Keetae entoki nagol to Laitoriani? Ore te nkata nageluno kaashukokino te nkata oloirujuruj, naa ketum Sara enkayioni.” 
15  Kake etomikio Sara ajo, “Eitu nanu akueni,” amu etureishe. Kake etiaka, ninye “A-a esipa itakuenia iyie.”

Etoomonoko Abraham Sodom olng'ur


16  Neinyototo lelo tung'ana te ine neing'or enkalo e Sodom neiriamariyie Abraham ninche aitarioo. 
17  Nejo Olaitoriani, “Kaisudorie Abraham embae netaa kaas, 
18  amaa adolita ajo ore Abraham naa keaku olosho kitok magilani, ore iloshon pooki le nkop kemayian ate te ninye? 
19  A'a, amu ategelua ninye peyie atum aitanapa nkera enyena olmarei lenye osuju ninye meibung'a orrekie lo Laitoriani eas isupati o sipat, peyie etum Olaitoriani ayaki Abraham imbaa naaisiligie ninye.” 
20  Metaa nejoki Olaitoriani, “Ore amu etaa olkiyioi sapuk te nkaraki Sodom o Gomora, netaa torrok oleng ing'ok tiatua 
21  e kadoyio alo aing'or tenaa ketaasa te risioroto olkiyioi oewuo enatii, naa tenemeneijia, nayiolou.”


22  Neibelekenya iltung'ana te ine, nepuo aaitoriokino enkalo e Sodom. Kake eitirring'e Abraham aitashe te dukuya Olaitoriani. 
23  Nenyiku Abraham nejo, “Amaa doi aindaikie isupati tenebo iltorrok? 
24  Amaa naaji te netii iltung'ana onom supati atua ina anasa, indim aidakie ewueji pooki nimipalie lelo supati onom otii atua? 
25  Metalakuana ena bae te iyie pee mias ena bae, aar metuata isupati o ltorrok, eji metaa kenyaanyuk osupat o ltorrono! Metalakuana ina bae te iyie! Amaa ilo oiguanare enkop pooki aimeas esipata?” 
26  Nejo Olaitoriani, “Tenatum tiatua Sodom iltung'ana onom ooitashe too sipat, naa kapal enkanasa pooki te nkaraki ninche.” 
27  Newal Abraham ajo, “Ing'ura ajo, ayaua kewan peyie airorie Olaitoriani, nara nanu enterit o nkuruon. 
28  Amaa sa teneng'oru imiet te onom le lelo ooitashe too sipat, indaikie enkanasa pooki enkaraki natong'oro imiet.” Nejo Olaitoriani, “Maidaikie ninye tenainepu artam o miet te ine.” 
29  Neitoki ake airorie ninye ejo, “Oo tenaa artam etumi te ine?” Neng'amaaa ajoki, “Ore enkaraki lelo artam, maas ina.” 
30  Neitoki Abraham ajo, “Oi mincho Olaitoriani egoro naa kairo. Oo tenaa tomoni oni etumi te ine?” Newal ninye, “Maas nanu ina tenatum tomoni uni te ine.” 
31  Nejo Abraham, “Ing'ura ajo ayaua kewan airorie Olaitoriani. Oo tenaa tikitam etumi te ine?” Newaliki ninye ajoki, “Ore tenkaraki lelo tikitam maidaikie ninye.” 
32  Neitoki Abraham ajo, “Oi mincho Olaitoriani egoro, naa kairo ena ae nabo ake. Oo tenetumi tomon te ine.” Newaliki ninye ajoki, “Ore enkaraki e lelo tomon maidaikie nanu ninye.” 
33  Nelo Olaitoriani aing'uaa ine, eidipa airorie Abraham. Nerrinyo Abraham alo ewueji enye.

